  <identification>
    <creator type="composer">Words: Martin Luther, 1541. Translated by Richard Massie, 1854.
Music: 'Christ, Unser Herr' Johann Walter, 1524.
Setting: composite from "Kern des Deutschen Kirchengesangs", 1855 and "Mehrstimmiges ChoralBuch", 1906.
copyright: public domain.  This score is a part of the Open Hymnal Project, 2006 Revision.</creator>
