      <encoder>abc2xml version 268</encoder>
      <software>https://wim.vree.org/svgParse/abc2xml.html</software>
      <encoding-date>2026-07-21</encoding-date>
    </encoding>
    <source>Music source: 'Evangelical Lutheran Hymn Book' Edition of 1931 Hymn 401.
Arrangement composite from "Kern des Deutschen Kirchengesangs", 1855 ed. Dr. Fridrich Layriz hymn 18 and "Mehrstimmiges ChoralBuch", 1906 Hymn #31, page 22 Ed. Karl Brauer.</source>
